trans-unit.source: An abstract class that represents a single query request to [!INCLUDE[ssAstoria](~/add/includes/ssastoria-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: En abstrakt klasse som representerer en forespørsel om én spørring [!INCLUDE[ssAstoria](~/add/includes/ssastoria-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: No public constructors are defined on this class.
trans-unit.target: Ingen offentlig konstruktør er definert for denne klassen.

trans-unit.source: Object instances are created by using <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceContext.CreateQuery%2A> or <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceContext.CreateQuery%2A> on the <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceContext> class.
trans-unit.target: Objektforekomster av er opprettet ved hjelp av <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceContext.CreateQuery%2A>eller <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceContext.CreateQuery%2A>på <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceContext>klasse.</xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceContext> </xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceContext.CreateQuery%2A> </xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceContext.CreateQuery%2A>

trans-unit.source: Asynchronously sends a request to execute the data service query.
trans-unit.target: Asynkront sender en forespørsel om å kjøre tjenesten dataspørring.

trans-unit.source: The returned <xref:System.IAsyncResult> object is used to determine when the asynchronous operation has completed.
trans-unit.target: Det returnerte <xref:System.IAsyncResult>objektet brukes til å bestemme når den asynkrone operasjonen er fullført.</xref:System.IAsyncResult>

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Asynchronous Operations](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, se [asynkrone operasjoner](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: The BeginExecute method uses the same semantics as the <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceQuery.Execute%2A> method, however BeginExecute asynchronously sends the request so that the call does not block processing while waiting for the results from the service.
trans-unit.target: Metoden BeginExecute bruker samme semantikk som den <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceQuery.Execute%2A>metoden, men BeginExecute asynkront sender forespørselen slik at kallet ikke blokkerer behandling under venting på resultater fra tjenesten.</xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceQuery.Execute%2A>

trans-unit.source: According to the standard begin-end asynchronous pattern, the provided callback is invoked when query results are retrieved.
trans-unit.target: I henhold til standard begin-end asynkrone mønsteret, er angitt tilbakeringing aktiveres når spørringsresultater hentes.

trans-unit.source: Delegate to invoke when results are available for client consumption.
trans-unit.target: Representanten for å aktivere når resultater er tilgjengelig for forbruk av klienten.

trans-unit.source: User-defined state object passed to the callback.
trans-unit.target: Brukerdefinerte tilstand objekt sendt til tilbakeringing.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.IAsyncResult> object that is used to track the status of the asynchronous operation.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.IAsyncResult>objekt som brukes til å spore statusen for den asynkrone operasjonen.</xref:System.IAsyncResult>

trans-unit.source: Called to complete the asynchronous operation of executing a data service query.
trans-unit.target: Kalles for å fullføre den asynkrone operasjonen for kjøring av en dataspørring for tjenesten.

trans-unit.source: The result from the <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceQuery.BeginExecute*> operation that contains the query results.
trans-unit.target: Resultatet fra den <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceQuery.BeginExecute*>operasjonen som inneholder resultatene av spørringen.</xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceQuery.BeginExecute*>

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601> that contains the results of the query operation.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601> som inneholder resultatene for spørringsoperasjonen.

trans-unit.source: When the data service returns an HTTP 404: Resource Not Found error.
trans-unit.target: Når data service returnerer en HTTP-404: Finner ikke ressursen feil.

trans-unit.source: Executes the query against the data service.
trans-unit.target: Utfører spørringen mot vertstjenesten.

trans-unit.source: The Execute method is used to execute the given data service query.
trans-unit.target: Execute-metoden brukes til å kjøre spørringen angitte tjenesten.

trans-unit.source: The Execute method generates an HTTP GET request that is set to the data service.
trans-unit.target: Execute-metoden genererer en HTTP GET-forespørsel som er satt til vertstjenesten.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601> that contains the results of the query operation.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601> som inneholder resultatene for spørringsoperasjonen.

trans-unit.source: When the data service returns an HTTP 404: Resource Not Found error.
trans-unit.target: Når data service returnerer en HTTP-404: Finner ikke ressursen feil.

trans-unit.source: Represents an expression that contains the query to the data service.
trans-unit.target: Representerer et uttrykk som inneholder spørringen til vertstjenesten.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Linq.Expressions.Expression> object that represents the query.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Linq.Expressions.Expression>objektet som representerer spørringen.</xref:System.Linq.Expressions.Expression>

trans-unit.source: Represents the query provider instance.
trans-unit.target: Representerer spørringen leverandøren-forekomst.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Linq.IQueryProvider> representing the data source provider.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Linq.IQueryProvider>som representerer datakilden dataleverandøren.</xref:System.Linq.IQueryProvider>

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator> object that can be used to iterate through the collection returned by the query.
trans-unit.target: Henter den <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator>objekt som kan brukes til å gå gjennom samlingen returnert av spørringen.</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator>

trans-unit.source: Enumerators can be used to read the data in the collection, but they cannot be used to modify the underlying collection.
trans-unit.target: Enumeratorene kan brukes til å lese data i samlingen, men de kan ikke brukes til å endre den underliggende samlingen.

trans-unit.source: An enumerator over the query results.
trans-unit.target: En opplisting over resultatene av spørringen.
